## How It Flows Together

```
User Goal
   │
   ▼
[Planner] → Breaks goal into subtasks with dependencies
   │
   ▼
[ReAct Loop per subtask]
   ├── THINK: Reason about what to do next (CoT)
   ├── ACT:   Call a tool or API
   ├── OBSERVE: Read the result
   └── CHECK: Run business rule validation
        ├── PASS → Move to next subtask
        ├── FAIL → Retry / branch / escalate
        └── BLOCKED → Human-in-the-loop
   │
   ▼
[Aggregator] → Combines results, generates final response
```

