## Key Design Patterns

| Pattern | Purpose |
|---|---|
| **ReAct** | Interleave reasoning + tool calls |
| **Plan-and-Execute** | Plan all steps upfront, then execute |
| **Reflection / Critic** | A second LLM pass that reviews the agent's output |
| **Self-consistency** | Sample multiple reasoning paths, pick the most common answer |
| **Supervisor + Subagents** | One orchestrator delegates to specialized agents |

