## Popular Frameworks That Implement This

- **LangGraph** — graph-based stateful agent workflows with conditional edges
- **AutoGen** — multi-agent conversation and task delegation
- **CrewAI** — role-based agent teams with defined goals
- **Semantic Kernel** — Microsoft's planner + plugin architecture
- **Anthropic tool use + prompt chaining** — native building block for all of the above

The most robust production systems combine **structured outputs** (so checks are reliable), **explicit state machines** (so workflows are auditable), and **human escalation paths** (so failures don't silently propagate).

